Suddenly, the world

08:58.780 --> 09:01.692
Seems such a perfect place

09:01.940 --> 09:03.532
My dear, a little frog!

09:03.820 --> 09:05.776
Suddenly it moves

09:06.020 --> 09:09.012
With such a perfect grace

09:10.260 --> 09:13.616
Suddenly my life doesn't...

09:13.900 --> 09:16.334
...seem such a waste

09:17.940 --> 09:21.012
It all revolves around you

09:23.020 --> 09:24.897
And there's no mountain

09:25.180 --> 09:27.091
Too high

09:27.460 --> 09:30.975
