09:31.260 --> 09:34.297
Sing out this song
And I'll be...

09:34.620 --> 09:37.373
...there by your side

09:38.500 --> 09:40.695
Storm clouds may gather

09:41.060 --> 09:44.257
And stars may collide

09:47.900 --> 09:49.219
But I love you

09:49.820 --> 09:51.253
I love you

