Till my dying day

11:35.540 --> 11:37.132
l don't like this ending.

11:42.180 --> 11:43.932
Don't like the ending?

11:44.140 --> 11:46.529
Why would the courtesan choose...

11:46.740 --> 11:49.937
...a penniless sitar player
over the maharajah...

11:50.180 --> 11:55.049
...who is offering a lifetime of
security? That's real love.

11:55.260 --> 11:58.536
Once the sitar player
has satisfied his lust...

11:58.740 --> 12:00.935
...he will leave her with nothing.

12:01.180 --> 12:04.889
l suggest that in the end,
the courtesan choose the maharajah.

12:05.140 --> 12:06.937
But, but.... Sorry.

12:08.180 --> 12:11.616
That ending does not uphold
the Bohemian ideals of...

12:11.900 --> 12:13.572
...truth, beauty, freedom--

12:13.780 --> 12:16.135
l don't care about
your ridiculous dogma!

12:16.860 --> 12:19.454
Why shouldn't the courtesan
choose the maharajah?

12:19.660 --> 12:21.730
Because she doesn't love you!

12:27.580 --> 12:28.569
Him.

12:30.820 --> 12:32.936
Him. She doesn't love...

12:33.260 --> 12:34.852
...she doesn't love him.

12:39.860 --> 12:41.452
Now l see.

12:49.860 --> 12:50.975
Monsieur Zidler.

12:51.300 --> 12:53.768
This ending will be rewritten...

12:54.580 --> 12:57.777
...with the courtesan choosing
the maharajah...

12:58.900 --> 13:02.415
