that will be quite impossible.

13:12.580 --> 13:13.899
Harold.

13:15.700 --> 13:19.329
The poor Duke is
being treated appallingly.

13:20.820 --> 13:24.733
These silly writers let their
imaginations run away with them.

13:30.260 --> 13:32.216
Why don't you and l...

13:33.340 --> 13:35.092
...have a little supper?

13:37.460 --> 13:39.530
Then afterwards...

13:40.660 --> 13:45.097
...we can let Monsieur Zidler know
how we would prefer the story to end.

13:53.580 --> 13:55.332
Thank you, Elizabeth.

13:57.140 --> 13:59.176
l don't want you to sleep with him.

14:01.580 --> 14:03.616
