14:16.700 --> 14:20.613
You promised me
you wouldn't be jealous.

14:26.020 --> 14:27.817
lt will be all right.

14:28.180 --> 14:29.898
Yes, it will.

14:31.820 --> 14:33.378
He's waiting.

14:47.660 --> 14:48.934
Come...

14:50.260 --> 14:53.457
... what may

15:08.180 --> 15:09.738
Come what may.

15:20.620 --> 15:23.339
She had gone to the tower
to save us all.

15:24.980 --> 15:26.538
And for our part...

15:27.260 --> 15:30.297
... we could do nothing but wait.

15:34.820 --> 15:38.699
My dear Duke. l hope l have not
kept you waiting.

15:59.500 --> 16:02.537
Don't worry, Shakespeare.
You'll get your ending.

16:02.740 --> 16:04.651
Once the Duke gets his...

16:04.980 --> 16:07.096
...end in.

16:08.140 --> 16:09.289
Nini. No, no.

16:10.420 --> 16:12.251
Keep your hands off me!

16:18.620 --> 16:22.374
Never fall in love with a woman
who sells herself.

16:22.580 --> 16:24.650
lt always ends bad!

16:32.060 --> 16:34.858
The boy has a ridiculous obsession
with me.

16:35.700 --> 16:39.534
l indulge his fantasy
because he's talented.

16:39.860 --> 16:44.092
We need him...but only
until tomorrow night.

16:45.300 --> 16:47.336
We have a dance...

16:53.740 --> 16:56.379
...in the brothels of Buenos Aires.

17:11.980 --> 17:13.299
lt tells the story...

17:18.579 --> 17:20.172
...of a prostitute...

17:36.580 --> 17:38.536
...and a man...

17:40.540 --> 17:43.054
...who falls in love...

17:44.980 --> 17:46.538
...with her.

18:02.060 --> 18:03.288
First...

18:03.500 --> 18:05.252
...there is desire!

18:11.540 --> 18:13.292
Then...passion!

18:20.500 --> 18:22.536
Then suspicion!

18:27.260 --> 18:30.138
Jealousy! Anger! Betrayal!

18:30.900 --> 18:33.778
When love is for the highest bidder,
there is no trust.

18:34.140 --> 18:36.176
Without trust, there is no love!

18:37.860 --> 18:38.975
Jealousy--

18:39.700 --> 18:41.452
--yes, jealousy--

18:42.500 --> 18:45.298
--will drive you mad!

18:48.820 --> 18:50.731
Roxanne

18:52.220 --> 18:56.054
