Sell your body to the night

19:23.420 --> 19:26.730
His eyes upon your face

19:27.620 --> 19:31.249
His hand upon your hand

19:31.860 --> 19:34.579
His lips caress your skin

19:36.060 --> 19:41.214
It's more than I can stand

