20:20.460 --> 20:23.054
...you will no longer be
a cancan dancer...

20:23.940 --> 20:25.134
...but an actress.

20:26.900 --> 20:28.333
l will make you...

20:30.140 --> 20:31.414
...a star.

20:40.060 --> 20:41.618
Accept it...

20:42.140 --> 20:45.928
...as a gift from this maharajah
to his courtesan.

20:49.420 --> 20:50.614
And....

20:52.580 --> 20:54.218
And the ending?

20:57.460 --> 21:01.419
Let Zidler keep his fairy-tale ending.

