l see.

22:10.740 --> 22:13.777
lt's our very own
penniless sitar player.

22:17.260 --> 22:19.615
-My dear Duke--
-Silence!

22:23.220 --> 22:25.256
You made me...

22:25.460 --> 22:27.530
...believe that you loved me!

22:41.460 --> 22:44.816
Why does my...

22:45.180 --> 22:47.694
...heart cry?

22:48.820 --> 22:51.095
Feelings...

22:52.060 --> 22:55.416
...I can't fight

24:08.980 --> 24:12.370
l couldn't.
l couldn't go through with it.

24:12.580 --> 24:17.449
l saw you there, and l felt
differently and l couldn't pretend.

24:18.140 --> 24:20.370
And the Duke, he saw!

24:20.820 --> 24:22.458
He saw and he--

24:25.780 --> 24:27.691
Christian, l love you.

24:28.060 --> 24:29.857
lt's okay.

24:30.140 --> 24:33.337
l couldn't do it. l didn't want to
pretend anymore.

24:33.620 --> 24:36.054
l didn't want to lie. l don't.

24:36.660 --> 24:39.220
And he knows. He knows and he--

24:39.540 --> 24:42.293
You don't have to pretend anymore.
We'll leave.

24:42.820 --> 24:44.492
We'll leave tonight.

24:44.820 --> 24:46.253
Leave?

24:48.180 --> 24:49.613
But the show--

24:50.300 --> 24:51.858
l don't care.

24:52.060 --> 24:54.051
l don't care about the show.

24:56.060 --> 24:59.689
