We have each other.

25:10.420 --> 25:13.298
Chocolat, take Satine to
her dressing room to pack.

25:13.500 --> 25:16.333
-No one must see you.
-l understand.

25:16.660 --> 25:19.697
Darling, you go and pack.
l'll be waiting.

25:23.940 --> 25:25.009
lt's the boy.

25:25.220 --> 25:28.849
He has bewitched her with words.

25:29.060 --> 25:32.336
l want her back, Zidler. Find her.

25:34.380 --> 25:35.369
Tell her...

25:36.820 --> 25:40.210
...that the show will end my way...

25:40.540 --> 25:44.215
...and she will come to me
when the curtain falls...

25:46.580 --> 25:48.810
...or l'll have the boy killed.

25:49.620 --> 25:50.735
Killed?

25:56.660 --> 25:57.934
Killed.

26:08.660 --> 26:10.730
Forgive the intrusion, cherub.

26:11.620 --> 26:12.973
You're wasting your time.

26:13.220 --> 26:14.653
You don't understand.

26:15.140 --> 26:17.779
The Duke is going to kill Christian.

26:20.300 --> 26:22.256
He is insanely jealous.

26:22.580 --> 26:25.572
