27:09.500 --> 27:14.699
We're going away from you, away from
the Duke, away from the Moulin Rouge!

27:15.380 --> 27:16.972
Goodbye, Harold.

27:17.460 --> 27:19.052
You're dying, Satine.

27:24.300 --> 27:25.858
You're dying.

27:35.860 --> 27:36.929
Another trick?

27:37.140 --> 27:40.496
No, my love.
The doctor told us.

27:42.620 --> 27:43.609
Marie?

27:59.780 --> 28:01.372
l'm dying.

28:08.060 --> 28:10.210
I was a fool...

28:10.980 --> 28:12.254
...to...

28:13.540 --> 28:15.178
...believe

28:17.700 --> 28:19.611
