28:21.100 --> 28:24.888
...to believe

28:27.180 --> 28:28.738
It all...

28:29.100 --> 28:33.378
...ends today

28:34.380 --> 28:36.735
Yes, it all...

28:37.100 --> 28:39.136
...ends...

28:41.580 --> 28:44.572
...today

28:47.740 --> 28:49.856
Send Christian away.

28:50.900 --> 28:52.731
Only you can save him.

28:59.340 --> 29:01.092
He'll fight for me.

29:02.060 --> 29:04.858
Unless he believes you don't love him.

29:07.500 --> 29:12.574
You're a great actress, Satine.
Make him believe you don't love him.

29:15.740 --> 29:17.617
Use your talent to save him.

29:18.980 --> 29:20.413
Hurt him.

29:21.700 --> 29:23.611
Hurt him to save him.

29:25.220 --> 29:27.131
There is no other way.

29:28.380 --> 29:31.577
The show must go on, Satine.

29:32.660 --> 29:35.254
We're creatures of the underworld.

29:35.940 --> 29:38.215
We can't afford to love.

29:40.900 --> 29:44.575
Today's...

29:44.900 --> 29:47.619
...the day...

29:48.580 --> 29:53.096
... when dreaming...

29:54.980 --> 29:59.610
...ends

30:06.820 --> 30:09.095
Another hero...

30:10.220 --> 30:12.893
...another mindless crime

30:13.700 --> 30:15.770
Behind the curtain...

30:16.740 --> 30:19.174
...in the pantomime

